OL,5, A new law will be introduced on        
OL,6, Wednesday to clear the names of the    
OL,7, hundreds of sub-postmasters wrongly    
OL,8, convicted in the Post Office scandal.  
OL,10,FThe legislation is expected to clear   
OL,11,Fthe majority of victims in England and 
OL,12,FWales by the end of July.              
OL,14,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak said it is  
OL,15,F"an important step forward in finally  
OL,16,Fclearing" hundreds of sub-postmasters. 
OL,18,FThose wrongly convicted will get an    
OL,19,Foption to settle for #600,000, without 
OL,20,Fthe need to bring a formal claim.      
